TEXT.TITLE: UNICORP AMERICAN <UAC> IN JOINT VENTURE
TEXT.BODY: Unicorp American Corp said it has formed a joint venture with Sybedon Corp, a New York real estate investment banking firm, to pursue real estate projects. It said a total of 20 mln dlrs is being committed to the joint venture. Reuter
